            <![CDATA[ <p><b>Financial Defense for Industrial Contractors Act or the FDIC Act </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation to begin proceedings for terminating the insured status of large depository institutions that deny banking services to federal contractors that otherwise qualify for such services. </p>]]>
